Package: capek
Type: Package
Title: Karel Capek's Novels
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Petr", "Simecek", email = "simecek@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Data package with full texts for Karel Capek's 6 completed novels (in Czech), 
    ready for text analysis. These novels are "Tovarna na absolutno", "Krakatit",
    "Hordubal", "Povetron", "Obecejny zivot", and "Valka s mloky". The package is highly
    inspired by Julia Silge's package `janeaustenr`.
URL: https://github.com/simecek/capek
BugReports: https://github.com/simecek/capek/issues
Suggests: dplyr
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
